// ****************************************************************************
// Method: ExtrudeAttributes::FieldsEqual
//
// Purpose:
//   This method compares two fields and return true if they are equal.
//
// Note:       Autogenerated by xml2atts.
//
// Programmer: xml2atts
// Creation:   omitted
